    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, a masterpiece of engineering equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit delivers a linear power band culminating in a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-fast M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT) and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring surgical precision during corner exit. The chassis maintains its structural integrity, supported by M-specific suspension geometry and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for optimized damping rates. While exhibiting honest wear commensurate with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a pure analog connection for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak BMW M-division performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
