      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with its signature eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing aluminum subframes and a multi-link rear setup to maintain optimal camber under lateral load. Recent service includes rod bearing prophylaxis and throttle actuator replacement, addressing the critical maintenance items of this high-performance platform. While showing minor signs of road use, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain sharp, offering an visceral, naturally aspirated driving experience.",
